118
00:06:12,420 --> 00:06:12,900
You can do this!

119
00:06:14,100 --> 00:06:14,540
Come on!

120
00:06:14,540 --> 00:06:15,140
I can't do it.

121
00:06:16,660 --> 00:06:17,300
I'm finished.

122
00:06:19,180 --> 00:06:20,020
Mr. Zhan.

123
00:06:20,620 --> 00:06:21,660
Master Qin told Miss Si

124
