125
00:06:23,300 --> 00:06:24,940
I was told to supervise you.

126
00:06:25,140 --> 00:06:26,140
I can't do it anymore.

127
00:06:27,100 --> 00:06:28,020
I could get crippled.

128
00:06:32,580 --> 00:06:33,740
Who do we have here?

129
00:06:35,020 --> 00:06:35,659
What happened

130
00:06:35,659 --> 00:06:37,260
over the past few days while I was away?

131
00:06:40,780 --> 00:06:41,659
Why are you here?

132
00:06:42,620 --> 00:06:43,620
To make fun of me?

133
00:06:43,940 --> 00:06:45,940
Jiang Zhan, don't be disheartened.

134
00:06:46,340 --> 00:06:47,620
Jiang Si asked me

135
00:06:47,980 --> 00:06:49,980
to teach you a few self-defense moves

136
00:06:50,260 --> 00:06:52,020
to make up for the lessons
Master Qin missed.

137
00:06:53,420 --> 00:06:54,140
This is insane.

138
00:06:55,100 --> 00:06:57,580
My sister must have gone insane!

139
00:06:58,340 --> 00:06:59,060
Chuchu.

140
00:06:59,820 --> 00:07:01,140
Do me a favor.

141
00:07:01,660 --> 00:07:02,780
Knock me out now.

142
00:07:03,100 --> 00:07:04,220
I can't take it anymore.

143
00:07:04,460 --> 00:07:06,100
Enough whining. Do as I say.

144
00:07:06,540 --> 00:07:08,140
We start practicing now.

145
00:07:08,380 --> 00:07:08,980
Practice?

146
00:07:09,540 --> 00:07:11,020
I've had enough of this!

147
00:07:11,500 --> 00:07:12,020
Fine!

148
00:07:12,020 --> 00:07:13,860
I'll do whatever you say!

149
00:07:20,180 --> 00:07:20,940
Today,

150
00:07:21,940 --> 00:07:22,900
