151
00:07:25,260 --> 00:07:27,100
What is going on now?

152
00:07:28,220 --> 00:07:28,820
I know

153
00:07:28,900 --> 00:07:29,740
you've used up

154
00:07:29,740 --> 00:07:30,860
a lot of energy lately.

155
00:07:31,340 --> 00:07:32,659
We martial artists

156
00:07:32,780 --> 00:07:33,700
