157
00:07:34,220 --> 00:07:35,300
Do not get hasty

158
00:07:35,540 --> 00:07:36,940
unless you want to get weaker.

159
00:07:37,700 --> 00:07:39,140
My way of training starts

160
00:07:39,380 --> 00:07:41,380
