164
00:07:49,060 --> 00:07:49,659
Enough chitchat.

165
00:07:50,500 --> 00:07:50,820
Eat up.

166
00:07:52,820 --> 00:07:54,620
It's always nicer outside.

167
00:07:55,659 --> 00:07:56,780
Being grounded

168
00:07:56,780 --> 00:07:58,180
