169
00:07:59,100 --> 00:08:00,380
Cursed Jiang Si.

170
00:08:01,220 --> 00:08:03,140
I'll exact vengeance.

171
00:08:03,340 --> 00:08:03,740
Ji!

172
00:08:04,100 --> 00:08:04,700
Bring some liquor!

173
00:08:05,100 --> 00:08:05,420
Yes!

174
00:08:07,940 --> 00:08:08,900
Who is that?

175
00:08:09,660 --> 00:08:10,460
Madam Xiao,

176
00:08:10,980 --> 00:08:12,740
I heard that is Miss Si's friend.

177
00:08:12,940 --> 00:08:13,900
The name is Lu Chuchu.

178
00:08:14,620 --> 00:08:15,820
Lu Chuchu?

179
00:08:18,300 --> 00:08:19,900
She is a girl?

180
00:08:20,700 --> 00:08:21,580
Why would a girl

181
00:08:21,580 --> 00:08:22,620
dress up like that?

182
00:08:23,740 --> 00:08:24,740
She is clearly

183
00:08:24,740 --> 00:08:25,980
not from a proper family.

184
00:08:26,340 --> 00:08:28,060
She is a vagabond for sure.

185
00:08:31,300 --> 00:08:32,179
Jiang Si.

186
00:08:33,299 --> 00:08:34,860
While I was grounded,

187
00:08:35,100 --> 00:08:36,059
she planted another spy

188
00:08:36,059 --> 00:08:37,620
in the Jiang family.

189
00:08:38,820 --> 00:08:42,100
It seems she is eager to replace me

190
00:08:42,100 --> 00:08:44,220
as the family head.

191
00:08:45,260 --> 00:08:45,900
Mother.

192
00:08:51,580 --> 00:08:53,300
Though you've been released,

193
00:08:53,580 --> 00:08:54,620
from now on,

194
00:08:54,980 --> 00:08:56,940
be mindful of your actions.

195
00:08:57,220 --> 00:08:59,940
Do not make the same mistake again.

196
00:09:00,340 --> 00:09:01,540
Indeed.

197
00:09:02,140 --> 00:09:03,380
I'll keep that in mind.

198
00:09:05,700 --> 00:09:06,460
Allow me.

199
00:09:10,500 --> 00:09:11,180
Mother.

200
00:09:13,780 --> 00:09:15,420
While I was sick,

201
00:09:16,180 --> 00:09:18,860
you've done so much for our family.

202
00:09:19,540 --> 00:09:21,580
I'm glad you appreciate it.

203
00:09:21,740 --> 00:09:24,900
While I was grounded,

204
00:09:25,300 --> 00:09:27,500
I reflected on a lot of things.

205
00:09:28,260 --> 00:09:31,340
I made some mistakes
with my way of educating the children.

206
00:09:31,860 --> 00:09:33,980
Unlike Miss Si, she has done a great job

207
00:09:34,300 --> 00:09:36,420
managing the family affairs.

208
00:09:36,740 --> 00:09:38,700
Even Zhan has become more diligent.

209
00:09:39,540 --> 00:09:41,180
I heard he has been

210
00:09:41,180 --> 00:09:42,540
practicing martial arts.

211
00:09:42,540 --> 00:09:44,820
They are fooling around.

212
00:09:45,820 --> 00:09:48,740
However, I noticed

213
00:09:48,900 --> 00:09:50,380
