214
00:09:50,460 --> 00:09:52,020
in the house.

215
00:09:52,540 --> 00:09:55,100
It even looks like she and Zhan

216
00:09:55,580 --> 00:09:58,340
are sharing an unusual relationship.

217
00:09:58,940 --> 00:10:00,340
Who is the girl?

218
00:10:01,420 --> 00:10:02,020
Nanny Li,

219
00:10:02,180 --> 00:10:03,300
who is that girl?

220
00:10:03,660 --> 00:10:04,540
Old Madam,

221
00:10:05,460 --> 00:10:07,180
she is Miss Si's friend,

222
00:10:07,340 --> 00:10:08,500
named Lu Chuchu.

223
00:10:08,780 --> 00:10:09,820
We don't know much about her.

224
00:10:10,580 --> 00:10:12,260
Ling'an has been crawling

225
00:10:12,460 --> 00:10:13,860
with refugees lately.

226
00:10:14,380 --> 00:10:16,780
Perhaps Lu Chuchu is one of them.

227
00:10:16,940 --> 00:10:17,820
A refugee?

228
00:10:18,100 --> 00:10:19,700
It doesn't matter who she is

229
00:10:20,180 --> 00:10:21,860
as long as she has a good heart

230
00:10:22,740 --> 00:10:24,020
and Zhan likes her.

231
00:10:24,900 --> 00:10:25,860
Indeed.

232
00:10:25,940 --> 00:10:27,140
You are totally right.

233
00:10:29,020 --> 00:10:30,220
On my way here,

234
00:10:30,660 --> 00:10:31,380
we actually

235
00:10:31,380 --> 00:10:33,100
saw Miss Chuchu.

236
00:10:34,060 --> 00:10:36,460
She does bear a hint of heroic poise.

237
00:10:37,020 --> 00:10:38,780
But she is a Han girl,

238
00:10:39,140 --> 00:10:39,860
why would she wear

239
00:10:39,860 --> 00:10:40,980
Hu clothes?

240
00:10:42,060 --> 00:10:42,620
Madam Xiao,

241
00:10:42,980 --> 00:10:44,820
just days ago, I saw her feeding

242
00:10:44,820 --> 00:10:46,180
Mr. Zhan

243
00:10:46,180 --> 00:10:47,380
in the garden.

244
00:10:47,620 --> 00:10:49,380
They were so intimate.

245
00:10:49,420 --> 00:10:50,740
She was like a vixen.

246
00:10:50,980 --> 00:10:52,380
Enough, stop talking.

247
00:10:52,900 --> 00:10:54,260
What is that nonsense about?

248
00:10:55,740 --> 00:10:56,900
Mother, calm down.

249
00:10:57,140 --> 00:10:58,100
Relax.

250
00:11:00,700 --> 00:11:03,780
If Nanny Li is right,

251
00:11:04,820 --> 00:11:07,020
the girl clearly has ulterior motives.

252
00:11:07,380 --> 00:11:09,100
Zhan's marriage will be
the least of our concerns.

253
00:11:09,540 --> 00:11:11,100
The reputation of our family

254
00:11:11,260 --> 00:11:12,740
is at stake.

255
00:11:12,860 --> 00:11:13,340
Enough.

256
00:11:13,860 --> 00:11:14,900
I've heard enough.

257
00:11:15,700 --> 00:11:17,420
A nameless girl of unknown background

258
00:11:17,580 --> 00:11:18,900
can't be married into our family!

259
00:11:19,460 --> 00:11:19,940
Yes.

260
00:11:30,220 --> 00:11:31,700
Greetings, Grandmother.

261
00:11:32,780 --> 00:11:34,260
Did you send for me?

262
00:11:34,500 --> 00:11:35,260
Zhan.

263
00:11:36,380 --> 00:11:39,620
What is your relationship

264
00:11:40,180 --> 00:11:41,660
with Miss Lu Chuchu?

265
00:11:43,140 --> 00:11:45,100
She is Commandant Yu's friend

266
00:11:45,380 --> 00:11:46,980
and also a friend of Si.

267
00:11:47,980 --> 00:11:51,180
How does Miss Chuchu

268
00:11:51,220 --> 00:11:53,260
also know Commandant Yu?

269
00:11:53,420 --> 00:11:54,140
I think

270
00:11:54,140 --> 00:11:55,420
they were childhood friends.

271
00:11:57,380 --> 00:11:58,420
Grandmother,

272
00:11:58,420 --> 00:11:59,900
why the sudden interest in her?

273
00:12:01,100 --> 00:12:02,900
My point is

274
00:12:03,780 --> 00:12:06,660
that if you truly like Miss Chuchu,

275
00:12:07,020 --> 00:12:08,900
you should've told me.

276
00:12:09,260 --> 00:12:11,220
But I want you to understand one thing.

277
00:12:11,740 --> 00:12:12,780
How much do you

278
00:12:12,780 --> 00:12:14,220
actually know about her?

279
00:12:14,900 --> 00:12:16,060
You know the rules

280
00:12:16,060 --> 00:12:16,940
of our family.

281
00:12:17,020 --> 00:12:18,460
A girl with no background

282
00:12:18,460 --> 00:12:20,260
and possibly ill intent

283
00:12:20,460 --> 00:12:21,260
can never be

284
00:12:21,260 --> 00:12:22,300
a member of the Jiang family.

285
00:12:22,380 --> 00:12:22,900
Grandmother.

286
00:12:23,860 --> 00:12:25,900
I think you are mistaken.

287
00:12:26,340 --> 00:12:27,140
First of all,

288
00:12:27,380 --> 00:12:28,500
Miss Chuchu and I

289
00:12:28,500 --> 00:12:29,820
are only friends.

290
00:12:30,100 --> 00:12:31,500
There's no romance involved.

291
00:12:31,940 --> 00:12:33,900
Secondly, she is

292
00:12:34,020 --> 00:12:35,620
the daughter
of the Pacification General.

293
00:12:35,620 --> 00:12:37,380
She is not nameless.

294
00:12:38,180 --> 00:12:38,710
What?

295
00:12:38,740 --> 00:12:39,780
